00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:45,440
 is the only person in a world where people do not wear

36
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:48,240
 their emotions on their face who will naturally

37
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,680
 kind of have a face that changes with her emotions.

38
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,240
 So that is the face-like glass.

39
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:54,520
 You can see everything going on in Neverfell's face.

40
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:57,000
 And she goes into this very strange city

41
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:00,000
 where there are delicacies that can change your memories,

42
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:04,880
 give you premonitions, bring back hidden past memories,

43
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:07,240
 but where no one can ever show emotions on their face

44
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:09,520
 unless they have a face that they were

45
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:13,120
 trained by a face myth to show that particular emotion.

46
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:16,960
 And so Neverfell kind of cannonballs into this world

