00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:25,880
 falls in with some of the other artisans of Coverna,

50
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,720
 ends up meeting the leader of Coverna,

51
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,960
 and generally discovering kind of the rot which sits

52
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,680
 at the heart of this underground world

53
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:36,360
 where the rich feast on precious delicacies

54
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,840
 and it's the underclass who keeps everything running.

55
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,800
 And everything is very kind of rigid and constrained,

