 and diligently carrying out your tasks.

185
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,480
 And if you're kind of an artisan,

186
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,960
 a middle-class sort of person,

187
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,680
 you get a fairly good range of faces

